{
  "stem": "323.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The house that I was born is still there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I went to the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There's a war memorial, where my two uncles who died fighting for Germany in World War I, they put their names.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had taken the names off, they put the names back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My nurse just died recently.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The woman who took care of me when I was a baby, she lived there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I went to visit her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so she, well she was-- she had-- she did what she had to do.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was never-- I mean, she stayed with us as long as she could.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then it was just-- but she was never a Nazi or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went back to Hochneukirch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the house that my-- that I spent many summers with my grandparents with.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The house was given back to us, by the German-- after, after the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we-- we gave the house to my aunt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because she was-- they were very, poor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She had the five kids.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I stayed with her in that house, in the garden.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the garden is still there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And everything is still there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, these really were good-- those were my good memories.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were, they were not bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Bielefeld or Lippstadt, I don't know anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, it changed so, it became so big, that I don't even know where-- I don't, don't know my way.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Stockholm has changed too, completely different.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The first time I went been back, and I saw this room that in my mind was this castle, it's like a little, little tiny room, with a bed and a bookcase and a desk.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And to me, that room was heaven.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's just what you remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
